## Description {#details}

Holds some extra information about a &lt;name&gt; that is being parsed.

This information is only pertinent if the &lt;name&gt; refers to an &lt;encoding&gt;.

Definition at line 2922 of file <a href="/docs/api/files/include/include/llvm/include/llvm/demangle/itaniumdemangle-h">ItaniumDemangle.h</a>.
